  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/455",
  "title": "Conditionally show/hide a widget",
  "body": "I was thinking, we might want to have a way to show/hide the widget depending on a condition.\n\nLet's say that I have two refinementLists. I show the first one by default and want to show the second one only if the first one is refined.\n\nThe api could look something like:\n\n```\ninstantsearch.widgets.anyWidget({\n    [...],\n    showOnly: function (helper) {\n      return helper.getRefinements('first-widget-attribute').length > 0;\n    }\n  })\n```\n\nWhat do you think ?\n",
